data.text:
CountryCode.org is your complete guide to make a call from anywhere in the world, to anywhere in the world. This page details Germany phone code.

The Germany country code 49 will allow you to call Germany from another country. Germany telephone code 49 is dialed after the IDD. Germany international dialing 49 is followed by an area code.

The Germany area code table below shows the various city codes for Germany. Germany country codes are followed by these area codes. With the complete Germany dialing code, you can make your international call.
